com.ericsson.jenkins.plugins.dashbeats.client

Class DashBeatsPublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericsson.jenkins.plugins.dashbeats.client.DashBeatsPublisher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatsPublisher

    public class DashBeatsPublisher
extends java.lang.Object
implements StatsPublisher
    This Class is responsible to publish data to the DashBeats server. It publish Jenkins BFA Stats to every widget within the dashboard. There are 5 widgets defined:
    • Welcome
    • Common Fault Causes
    • Latest Builds
    • Latest Failed Builds
    • Top Failed Jobs
    Created by ekongto on 2014-09-08.
